                <div>
                    <h3>Mobile GTD Strategy</h3>
                    <div style="margin: 20px 0;">
                        <h4>üéØ Primary Mobile Functions:</h4>
                        <ul style="line-height: 1.8;">
                            <li><strong>Capture:</strong> Voice notes, quick emails, photos of business cards</li>
                            <li><strong>Triage:</strong> Quick inbox processing (delete, flag, file)</li>
                            <li><strong>Context Actions:</strong> @Calls while commuting, @Errands while out</li>
                            <li><strong>Quick Responses:</strong> 2-minute rule items</li>
                            <li><strong>Calendar Review:</strong> Daily planning and scheduling</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div style="margin: 20px 0;">
                        <h4>üìµ What NOT to Do on Mobile:</h4>
                        <ul style="line-height: 1.8;">
                            <li>Complex email composition</li>
                            <li>Detailed project planning</li>
                            <li>Weekly reviews (needs bigger screen)</li>
                            <li>System setup and configuration</li>
                            <li>Lengthy document editing</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
