        <div class="slide" id="slide6">
            <h2>üìã Your Implementation Action Plan</h2>
            
            <div class="insight-box">
                <h3>Phase-by-Phase Implementation Strategy</h3>
                <p>Don't try to build everything at once. Follow this proven implementation sequence for sustainable success.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="setup-steps">
                <div class="setup-step">
                    <h4>Week 1: Foundation Setup</h4>
                    <ul style="margin: 10px 0 10px 20px;">
                        <li>Clean up existing inbox and folders</li>
                        <li>Set up basic GTD categories (@Calls, @Computer, etc.)</li>
                        <li>Configure mobile Outlook with sync settings</li>
                        <li>Establish daily 20-minute processing time</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><strong>Goal:</strong> Get the basic system running</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="setup-step">
                    <h4>Week 2: Workflow Development</h4>
                    <ul style="margin: 10px 0 10px 20px;">
                        <li>Create email processing rules and automation</li>
                        <li>Set up project tracking system</li>
                        <li>Implement 2-minute rule consistently</li>
                        <li>Begin using next action thinking</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><strong>Goal:</strong> Build processing habits</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="setup-step">
                    <h4>Week 3: Integration & Optimization</h4>
                    <ul style="margin: 10px 0 10px 20px;">
                        <li>Connect OneNote for project reference</li>
                        <li>Set up Teams integration for collaboration</li>
                        <li>Create weekly review calendar appointment</li>
                        <li>Optimize mobile workflows</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><strong>Goal:</strong> Enhance and integrate the system</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="setup-step">
                    <h4>Week 4: Advanced Features</h4>
                    <ul style="margin: 10px 0 10px 20px;">
                        <li>Implement Power Automate workflows</li>
                        <li>Set up advanced search and filtering</li>
                        <li>Create custom Quick Steps</li>
                        <li>Conduct first complete weekly review</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><strong>Goal:</strong> Achieve system mastery</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="takeaway-highlight">
                <strong>Implementation Tip:</strong> Focus on building one habit at a time. Don't move to the next week until the current week's habits feel natural.
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Slide 7: Troubleshooting and Support -->
        <div class="slide" id="slide7">
            <h2>üîß Common Challenges and Solutions</h2>
            
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin: 30px 0;">
                <div style="background: #fef5e7; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; border-left: 5px solid #f6ad55;">
                    <h4>üö´ "IT Won't Let Me Install Anything"</h4>
                    <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Outlook is already approved! Use built-in features like categories, rules, and tasks. Everything you need is already there.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div style="background: #f0f9ff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; border-left: 5px solid #3b82f6;">
                    <h4>üì± "Mobile App Doesn't Sync"</h4>
                    <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Check sync settings in both desktop and mobile. Ensure categories and folders are set to sync across devices.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div style="background: #f0fdf4; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; border-left: 5px solid #10b981;">
                    <h4>‚è∞ "No Time for Daily Processing"</h4>
                    <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Start with 10 minutes. Use mobile for quick triage. Process during natural transition times (commute, coffee breaks).</p>
                </div>
                
                <div style="background: #fdf2f8; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; border-left: 5px solid #ec4899;">
                    <h4>ü§Ø "System Feels Overwhelming"</h4>
                    <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Simplify! Start with just inbox and 3 categories. Add complexity only when current system feels natural.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div style="background: #f5f3ff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; border-left: 5px solid #8b5cf6;">
                    <h4>üë• "Team Doesn't Use This System"</h4>
                    <p><strong>Solution:</strong> GTD is personal productivity. Use your system internally, communicate clearly with team. Lead by example.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div style="background: #ecfdf5; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; border-left: 5px solid #059669;">
                    <h4>üîÑ "Keep Falling Off Track"</h4>
                    <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Normal! "It's easy to get off track, and easy to get back on." Just restart your daily processing routine.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="interactive-section">
                <h3>üÜò Emergency Recovery Plan</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 15px;">When your system breaks down (and it will), follow this recovery sequence:</p>
                
                <div class="checklist-item" onclick="toggleChecklist(this)">
                    <div class="checklist-checkbox"></div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Don't Panic - This is Normal</strong><br>
                        <small>Even David Allen's system breaks down sometimes</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="checklist-item" onclick="toggleChecklist(this)">
                    <div class="checklist-checkbox"></div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Do a Quick Inbox Clear</strong><br>
                        <small>Just delete obvious junk and flag anything important</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="checklist-item" onclick="toggleChecklist(this)">
                    <div class="checklist-checkbox"></div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Schedule a Mini Weekly Review</strong><br>
                        <small>30 minutes to get back on track</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="checklist-item" onclick="toggleChecklist(this)">
                    <div class="checklist-checkbox"></div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Restart Daily Processing</strong><br>
                        <small>Begin tomorrow with fresh commitment</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="checklist-item" onclick="toggleChecklist(this)">
                    <div class="checklist-checkbox"></div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Simplify If Needed</strong><br>
                        <small>Remove complexity that's not serving you</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

